item.title: Episode 41 The Pads Go On!
item.description: The Boys are back, getting you ready for the new season as the Dogs put on the pads and start hitting. The University announces a fashion show for the new uniforms. Key players go down with injuries and others are lost to academics. Field turf still not finished and the fall scrimmage is moved to the practice field. Check us out at www.dogbytepodcast.com
